    "en": {
      "title": "A meeting of determined party leaders today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A meeting of determined party leaders has been called today (11) to discuss the future political affairs of the country.",
        "It has been informed that a meeting of party leaders will be held today at 2 pm under the chairmanship of Speaker Mahinda Yappa Abeywardhana.",
        "After President Gotabaya Rajapaksa steps down from the presidency on the 13th, the appointment of a new president and the formation of a new government will be discussed in today's special meeting of party leaders. (a)"
      ],
